{"tid":2081664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最近廚房好撚多細曱甴,比我用洗頭水射撚死左好多隻","createTime":"2020-06-27T11:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T12:44:32.000Z","uid":88737,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"219b6377bfa4a534b13a38a96912965a85772ce5","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"個廚房一直都有德國甲由既問題,天氣一熱就好活躍,效晚出廚房,我一直有放殺他死隻藥餌,而家發現佢地唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔敢係廚房噴殺蟲水只可以用手拍,有捐窿捐拉又好難拍中,拍中左就洗手好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網睇左D清潔劑溝水噴可以殺到,苜先試左洗潔精效用唔明顯,之後睇左條YOUTUBE片(唔比LINK)講洗頭水係最有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一試,真係好撚有用!!!射中左10秒內見效,我一晚做低左十幾廿隻<br />\n<br />\n配方:<br />\n<br />\n我係求其用rxjxxxx,1比20 至 1比30 咁溝水(我覺得應該用最平最common最chemical果D就最岩,唔好用果D天然)<br />\n<br />\n用噴花壺或津路水炮裝都得<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/27/YS3wQF.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F27%2FYS3wQF.jpeg&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=2ee7c5e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/27/YS3wQF.jpeg</a><br />\n<br />\n用法:<br />\n<br />\n對準目標,第一擊一定要快速連射,務求瞬間打濕晒目標同周圍,之後隻甲由就會係10秒內慢落黎,到時候可以補一槍等佢死得舒服D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係幾有用同幾好玩,但係都有D治標唔治本,唔知有無人有其他對付德國甲由既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW 7.1維園見"},{"pid":"eeaf1419804c217c46d9c42acd885b27a1466c1e","tid":2081664,"uid":201604,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"係咪歧視德國？"},{"pid":"c7bf1610bfe73e0a0fe808793ea4c8d10652e728","tid":2081664,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個廚房一直都有德國甲由既問題,天氣一熱就好活躍,效晚出廚房,我一直有放殺他死隻藥餌,而家發現佢地唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔敢係廚房噴殺蟲水只可以用手拍,有捐窿捐拉又好難拍中,拍中左就洗手好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網睇左D清潔劑溝水噴可以殺到,苜先試左洗潔精效用唔明顯,之後睇左條YOUTUBE片<span style=\"color: red;\">(唔比LINK)</span>講洗頭水係最有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一試,真係好撚有用!!!射中左10秒內見效,我一晚做低左十幾廿隻<br />\n<br />\n配方:<br />\n<br />\n我係求其用rxjxxxx,1比20 至 1比30 咁溝水(我覺得應該用最平最common最chemical果D就最岩,唔好用果D天然)<br />\n<br />\n用噴花壺或津路水炮裝都得<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/27/YS3wQF.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F27%2FYS3wQF.jpeg&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=2ee7c5e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/27/YS3wQF.jpeg</a><br />\n<br />\n用法:<br />\n<br />\n對準目標,第一擊一定要快速連射,務求瞬間打濕晒目標同周圍,之後隻甲由就會係10秒內慢落黎,到時候可以補一槍等佢死得舒服D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係幾有用同幾好玩,但係都有D治標唔治本,唔知有無人有其他對付德國甲由既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW 7.1維園見</blockquote><br />\n拉"},{"pid":"fba600276c0570b5a0abeb810f4d3432428a4b33","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"eeaf1419804c217c46d9c42acd885b27a1466c1e","tid":2081664,"uid":201604,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"係咪歧視德國？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"德國甲由 美國甲由唔係歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國武漢肺炎就係歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbb711233326604670586b18e446bb6a1e6fc56","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/27/GotdbS.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2