-06-27T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"用甲由屋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"聽講曱甴屋係殺死曱甴前會引到成屋都係曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"最怕係屋企已經一家大細住喺度,咁樣用曱甴屋係短期內將佢哋一網打盡嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n之前我屋企廚櫃都成日發現曱甴,放咗兩晚之後捉咗八九隻就唔再見有啦<br />\n<br />\n當然嗰啲及出入嘅位你都要保持清潔啦, 好似廚房嘅地台去水位一定要成日倒水入去<br />\n<br />\n之前有人推介用曱甴藥,我都聽過好有效"},{"pid":"5ca9d26d7b5a8a9beab2b3c08cf82f7c5315940b","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba7f14fa79400a268f87811600db3016b6f436eb","tid":2081664,"uid":64103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"用甲由屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"用緊，作用唔大，同埋放唔到上爐頭"},{"pid":"e5cfd30ba140ea4a8e471cbddf6a87d1fcdca1fd","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70546a9c87923be8e521140a05c76d33b8fca3b6","tid":2081664,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"試過用wd40"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:51:21.000Z","msg":"整到油林林"},{"pid":"70903eb756baeb974b8ee6b0dbfad1981a4c60b0","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"072495e0914f1a21f543b4905be2617d0ec4912c","tid":2081664,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:43:45.000Z","msg":"橡筋<br />\n鹽槍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:52:45.000Z","msg":"我之前都有諗鹽槍，但係睇佢好似只係夠力殺烏應<br />\n<br />\n成年德國甲由應該唔夠力"},{"pid":"b6a666d03e7bd181241ca66c7f5031ff157b508c","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be2f871f1d9f54ec9009558964db2a95a4ef02a2","tid":2081664,"uid":64103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e23ae5ffe106ed40aca5be333e792285b81d294","tid":2081664,"uid":194298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba7f14fa79400a268f87811600db3016b6f436eb","tid":2081664,"uid":64103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy