65da3c3","tid":2081664,"uid":46960,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d5026004a9390d1c49880ed06dc632570ac18e2e","tid":2081664,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"11353ce83ec3e6dbd88437bd67bc7ce9f9059b8b","tid":2081664,"uid":46960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"732caf960e962c547a7b737afcd297f0f95b767b","tid":2081664,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:30:15.000Z","msg":"你日日keep住射 之黎抹到仆街啦 我放堆月桂葉 兩星期換一次 一次10蚊 咁耐都未見過有黑警"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:42:07.000Z","msg":"邊度有月桂葉買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藥房?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"唔教你 問老母一定知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁七海去百佳睇下啦,<br />\nthx"},{"pid":"28337094a96989f39dcb5e783a00d03eaa72712c","tid":2081664,"uid":350688,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:49:22.000Z","msg":"還原基本步<br />\n每日用消毒水抹一次廚房有油污漬地方<br />\n盡量擺少啲雜物乾貨<br />\n根本唔洗咩曱甴屋殺蟲藥<br />\n否則只會治標不治本"},{"pid":"e9e650b5ff084bb8ae9933bf59fcc2ee7d20ff2c","tid":2081664,"uid":151343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"219b6377bfa4a534b13a38a96912965a85772ce5","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"個廚房一直都有德國甲由既問題,天氣一熱就好活躍,效晚出廚房,我一直有放殺他死隻藥餌,而家發現佢地唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔敢係廚房噴殺蟲水只可以用手拍,有捐窿捐拉又好難拍中,拍中左就洗手好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網睇左D清潔劑溝水噴可以殺到,苜先試左洗潔精效用唔明顯,之後睇左條YOUTUBE片(唔比LINK)講洗頭水係最有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一試,真係好撚有用!!!射中左10秒內見效,我一晚做低左十幾廿隻<br />\n<br />\n配方:<br />\n<br />\n我係求其用rxjxxxx,1比20 至 1比30 咁溝水(我覺得應該用最平最common最chemical果D就最岩,唔好用果D天然)<br />\n<br />\n用噴花壺或津路水炮裝都得<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/27/YS3wQF.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F27%2FYS3wQF.jpeg&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=2ee7c5e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/27/YS3wQF.jpeg</a><br />\n<br />\n用法:<br />\n<br />\n對準目標,第一擊一定要快速連射,務求瞬間打濕晒目標同周圍,之後隻甲由就會係10秒內慢落黎,到時候可以補一槍等佢死得舒服D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係幾有用同幾好玩,但係都有D治標唔治本,唔知有無人有其他對付德國甲由既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW 7.1維園見"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:50:49.000Z","msg":"最佳方法就係挑蛋。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WQp73jS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQp73jS.jpg&h=775f223e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"380bdad4bc78eb2dba6bc4df73266b178a1d496c","tid":2081664,"uid":151343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"殺下一代比現在更重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31819261ce7a9e36b2412c7917363858edd0ec3f","tid":2081664,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ddcda360b591e726c9da9b02de5c8f56213c13a","tid":2081664,"uid":135284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9ab890799a3b2919734b31b808cab7b18cdf369","tid":2081664,"uid":44569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"953453311a9479ead4c13167df7bde9576e29840","tid":2081664,"uid":135284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:31:33.000Z","msg":"焗完之後點知死係邊，去收屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:37:35.000Z","msg":"會出哂黎死<br />\n一返到屋企周圍都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:48:27.000Z","msg":"係咪要收晒啲衫入衣櫃，事後再要抹過晒所有家俬？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"佢聲稱唔使過水<br />\n不過食具同廚具最好洗過哂佢<br />\n同埋食物要包好封好<br />\n上個禮拜先炸左次<br />\n呢排唔知做咩有 d 細強"},{"pid":"4270018472eb