rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f4ec923db1931d9515648cab248c103688543d","tid":2081664,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e650b5ff084bb8ae9933bf59fcc2ee7d20ff2c","tid":2081664,"uid":151343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"219b6377bfa4a534b13a38a96912965a85772ce5","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"個廚房一直都有德國甲由既問題,天氣一熱就好活躍,效晚出廚房,我一直有放殺他死隻藥餌,而家發現佢地唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔敢係廚房噴殺蟲水只可以用手拍,有捐窿捐拉又好難拍中,拍中左就洗手好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網睇左D清潔劑溝水噴可以殺到,苜先試左洗潔精效用唔明顯,之後睇左條YOUTUBE片(唔比LINK)講洗頭水係最有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一試,真係好撚有用!!!射中左10秒內見效,我一晚做低左十幾廿隻<br />\n<br />\n配方:<br />\n<br />\n我係求其用rxjxxxx,1比20 至 1比30 咁溝水(我覺得應該用最平最common最chemical果D就最岩,唔好用果D天然)<br />\n<br />\n用噴花壺或津路水炮裝都得<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/27/YS3wQF.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F27%2FYS3wQF.jpeg&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=2ee7c5e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/27/YS3wQF.jpeg</a><br />\n<br />\n用法:<br />\n<br />\n對準目標,第一擊一定要快速連射,務求瞬間打濕晒目標同周圍,之後隻甲由就會係10秒內慢落黎,到時候可以補一槍等佢死得舒服D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係幾有用同幾好玩,但係都有D治標唔治本,唔知有無人有其他對付德國甲由既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW 7.1維園見"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:50:49.000Z","msg":"最佳方法就係挑蛋。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WQp73jS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQp73jS.jpg&h=775f223e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T01:04:34.000Z","msg":"點搵隻蛋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我搵極都係得屎"},{"pid":"eeebe62fb090ad887051a79a59313ede0ae1b067","tid":2081664,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"903b527da4bd333c47f72fe9d9c9d98a1404d412","tid":2081664,"uid":265840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31819261ce7a9e36b2412c7917363858edd0ec3f","tid":2081664,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ddcda360b591e726c9da9b02de5c8f56213c13a","tid":2081664,"uid":135284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:48:27.000Z","msg":"係咪要收晒啲衫入衣櫃，事後再要抹過晒所有家俬？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"佢聲稱唔使過水<br />\n不過食具同廚具最好洗過哂佢<br />\n同埋食物要包好封好<br />\n上個禮拜先炸左次<br />\n呢排唔知做咩有 d 細強"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T18:56:14.000Z","msg":"電器好似都要熄哂佢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係雪櫃冰格好多嘢唔插電好麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"雪櫃我照開"},{"pid":"e31f6fb6f90ef3521ca2601442011f01ebd9c64e","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5aa8f959214f2cde5152fb09ec8af4e5b7275a3","tid":2081664,"uid":194008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T19:38:53.000Z","msg":"去藥房買支 &ldquo;一點絕&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我用完屋企幾年都無曱甴出現<br />\n清屋企小強竇同時 要預防埋新小強從你鄰居屋企爬渠入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 百幾蚊好似有d貴"},{"pid":"5dcec93aefdd24748deeddddadd64e3817c8694d","tid":2081664,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"德國曱甴用曱甴煙霧係最有效"},{"pid":"afcdecf9cf0dbaeb7f0ade4b85f4c4068cefea23","tid":2081664,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dcec93aefdd24748deeddddadd64e3817c8694d","tid":2081664,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"德國曱